{"html":"<h2>Tactic(s)</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: Counter_Monotonicity<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: s<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;∀.*=&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;=&quot;&quot;zeyiufglgofzff&quot;&quot;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;&lt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;last\\(&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;DCtrIs\\(d,C&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;DCtr&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;mimou&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: IV_Uniqueness<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: s<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;=&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;&lt;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;last\\(&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;IV\\(&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: Key_IntegrityAndConfidentiality<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: s<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;CreateKey\\(ek,&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;</p><br/>\n","title":"Tactics"}